<h1>Post feed</h1>

<ul>
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
<img src="<%="#{post.picture}"%>">
<li><%= link_to User.find(post.user_id).name, user_path(post.user_id) %> cooked 
<%= link_to Recipe.find(post.recipe_id).name, recipe_path(post.recipe_id) %>
<br>

This chef gave a rating of <%=post.rating%> out of 5 for that recipe<br><br>
If you would like to comment on this post hit the following 
<%= button_to 'Check this post', post_path(post.id), method: :get %><br>
<%end%> </li>
</ul>